release_note: Change: You can now change directly to the tool you want to switch to. Bug fix: Fixed a bug that the UI slightly overlaps with Dynamic Island.
Bug fix: Fixed some UI bugs.
The eraser tool has been revived!

ver.3.0.2 Bug fix: Fixed minor UI bugs. ver.3.0.0 New Feature: Rectangle and Ellipse tools have been added! The background grid can now be turned on and off. Change: The Eraser tool has been removed for future functionality. If you want to delete a path please use the Selection tool or Undo. New App icon. Bug fix: Other minor fixes have been made.

New Feature: Rectangle and Ellipse tools have been added! The background grid can now be turned on and off. Change: The Eraser tool has been removed for future functionality. If you want to delete a path please use the Selection tool or Undo. New App icon. Bug fix: Other minor fixes have been made.
Bug fix: Fixed a bug that prevented some stylus pens from working.
Change: Changed that the selection tool selects objects completely enclosed only. Changed to display Yes No dialog when the new button is pressed.
Bug fix: Fixed a bug where the purchase screen would close as soon as it was opened when offline.
Bug fix: Fixed a bug that the title disappears when you tap the title of the document.

You can now list recently opened documents. Change: You can now move directly from the canvas screen to the folder list screen. You can now move directly from the canvas screen to the purchase screen. Changed some UI.

Added the selection tool! You can now select multiple paths and delete them all at once. Added ON OFF option for the pen pressure. If you are using the keyboard you can now create new document with cmd N undo with cmd Z and redo with cmd shift Z. Change: Changed the minimum size of the eraser. Changed that you cannot undo to the state before the document was loaded. Bug fix: Fixed some minor bugs.
Supported iOS 15. Changed the minimum supported OS to iOS 14.1. Changed the default page size to A1. Fixed some display bugs.
You can add a timestamp to a file name when exporting.
Bug fix: Fixed a crash bug.
Bug fix: Fixed a bug that unnecessary lines dust may be drawn when scrolling or zooming.
Fixed some minor bugs such as a bug that caused the display to collapse when the device orientation was changed while displaying gesture instructions.
You can now change the size of the pen and eraser. The GUI is hidden while writing.

Version 2 released! Blue Sketch has been upgraded! Can change the page size Can scale the page Can export the entire page The trash box has been implemented Can turn off on the function the app puts the device into a sleep state if you don t touch the screen for a certain period while the page is displayed Good news for Apple Pencil 2 users! Double tap the Apple Pencil to smoothly switch between pen and eraser Important Notice From this version adding pages will be paid content. Free gift for the first 20 pages! In addition you can use the documents you have created so far for free. Please support the developer.
Improved performance when using Apple Pencil.
Fixed that it is not case sensitive when sorting by title.
FIXED: Fixed a bug that first written line cannot be undone. Fixed a bug that sometimes an unintended straight line was drawn.
Improved performance.
NEW FEATURES: You can sort documents and folders in ascending or descending order. Save the sort settings of document and folder list. FIXED: Fixed a bug of UI.
FIXED: Fixed a bug that could not be erased with the eraser.

NEW FEATURES: Enhanced export function: Previously only PNG output was possible but now it is also possible to output in JPG and PDF format. Also you can output monochrome converted images. FIXED: Fixed the problem that the operation becomes heavy when writing heavily in one document.
NEW FEATURES: Added the option to use only Apple Pencil. FIXED: Fixed a crash bug when exporting and then saving an image.

Added two new features! Read only mode: While in read only mode you can disable writing and prevent erroneous operations. You can change the settings by tapping the title on the note screen. Copy documents: You can duplicate the document. Tap the copy button at the bottom right of the note screen to duplicate it.
Improved performance.
Improved writing and drawing comfort!
Bug Fixed: Fixed a bug that the eraser doesn t erase cleanly.
You can easily draw dotted and straight lines!
New Feature: You can organize your notes by folder!
Fixed bugs.
Modified the layout of the collection page.
You can title your canvas!
Fixed a bug of export function. Performance improvements.
Fixed to maintain aspect ratio when rotating canvas.
New: You can sort collections. Fix: Fixed a bug that the background became transparent when exporting images. Fixed the layout.
Fixed bugs.
Fixed bugs.
